    OpenSoaring Software <http://opensoaring.info>

This package provides the OpenSoaring set of tools and applications.

WHAT IS OPENSOARING

  OpenSoaring software provides a set of open source applications
  for glider clubs and pilots. These are mostly web based and mobile services
  for managing pilots and fleets, planning of instructors and machine
  assignment, flight planning and analysis, etc.

DOCUMENTATION

  Full documentation is available both in this package and online
  at <http://opensoaring.info/documentation>, provided in txt, pdf
  and html formats.

GETTING HELP

  If you are a user of any of our applications, please join the mailing
  list opensoaring-user@groups.google.com to get additional help from
  what is providing in the FAQ and documentation pages.
